@startuml
title Pipeline de Comunicación · Agente Virtual Inteligente

actor "Usuario" as User
participant "Unity Client" as Unity
participant "Captura de Audio\n(micrófono)" as Mic
participant "STT Service\n(local / cloud)" as STT
participant "LLM Service\n(local / cloud)" as LLM
participant "TTS Service\n(local / cloud)" as TTS
participant "Reproductor\n(Unity AudioSource)" as Speaker

User -> Mic : habla
Mic -> Unity : audio PCM
Unity -> STT : POST audio (REST / WebSocket)
STT --> Unity : texto transcrito (UTF-8) + WER esperado
Unity -> LLM : prompt + contexto + system prompt
note right of LLM
  Streaming token a token
  TTFT crítico para UX
end note
LLM --> Unity : tokens (stream) + usage
Unity -> Unity : agrega tokens y arma respuesta final
Unity -> TTS : texto a sintetizar (REST / WebSocket / gRPC)
TTS --> Unity : audio MP3/PCM (stream)
Unity -> Speaker : reproducir audio + sincronizar lip-sync
Speaker --> User : voz del agente

note over Unity, LLM
  En modo local el LLM corre vía Ollama
  (HTTP a localhost:11434). En modo cloud
  se usa OpenAI/Anthropic/Gemini/Groq.
end note

note over STT
  Modelos evaluados: whisper-1, Nova-3,
  AssemblyAI Best, Azure Standard,
  faster-whisper large-v3 (int8_float16)
end note

note over TTS
  Modelos evaluados: gpt-4o-mini-tts,
  eleven_multilingual_v2, Azure Neural,
  Google Neural2, Piper local
end note

@enduml
